											<h4 class="list-group-item-heading name" style="margin-top:10px;">Victoria</h4>
											<p class="list-group-item-text title">If you are from <b>DHHS Victoria</b>, please select here</p>
									    </div>												
									    <div class="x-table-cell-item" style="width: 20%">
											<img src="/ksLicensing/resources/default/images/arrow-right.png" class="pull-right x-icon">
